page.title: 20Credits
page.content:
This survey was carried out by children from Trimley St.Mary County Primary School and edited by the Headmaster.Work on Trimley Shore and the dock expansion was based on a project by Mr.Chris.Somerville's class.
The photographs were chosen from the collection of a parent,Mr.Paul Gill.
Thanks are due to the Public Relations Officer of Felixstowe Dock Company;the Warden and residents of Reeve Lodge,Trimley;Mr.Henry Birch of Bidwell's; the Trimley Postmaster, Mr.S.Moss;the Reception Staff of Eurosports Village, Shotley;the Rector of Trimley, Rev.C.Leffler and the Deputy Headteacher and children of Shotley County Primary School for meeting survey teams and answering their questions.
